quran[6{c,v,t}:
10,1,"a l- ray, yeh uss kitaab ki ayaat hain jo hikmat o Danish se labraiz hai"
10,2,kya logon ke liye yeh aik ajeeb baat ho gayi ke hum ne khud aُnhi mein se aik aadmi ko ishara kya ke ( ghaflat mein parre hue ) logon ko chonka day aur jo maan len un ko khushkhabri dide ke un ke liye unn ke rab ke paas sachhi izzat o sarfarazi hai? ( kya yahi woh baat hai jis par ) munkareen ne kaha ke yeh shakhs to khula jadugar hai ?
10,3,"haqeeqat yeh hai ke tumhara rab wohi khuda hai jis ne asmano aur zameen ko chay dinon mein peda kya, phir takhat hukoomat par jalva gir howa aur kaayenaat ka intizam chala raha hai koi Shafaat ( sifarish ) karne wala nahi ila yeh ke is ki ijazat ke baad Shafaat kere yahi Allah tumhara rab hai lehaza tum usi ki ibadat karo phir kya tum hosh mein nah aao ge ?"
10,4,"isi ki taraf tum sab ko palat kar jana hai, yeh Allah ka pakka wada hai be shak paidaiesh ki ibtida wohi karta hai, phir wohi dobarah peda kere ga, taakay jo log imaan laaye aur jinhon ne naik amal kiye un ko poooray insaaf ke sath jaza day, aur jinhon ne kufar ka tareeqa ikhtiyar kya woh kholta howa pani پییں aur dard naak saza bhgtin uss inkaar haq ki Padaash mein jo woh karte rahay"
10,5,wohi hai jis ne sooraj ko Ujyala banaya aur chaand ko chamak di aur chaand ke ghatney bherne ki manzilain theek theek muqarrar kar den taakay tum uss se barson aur tarikhon ke hisaab maloom karo Allah ne yeh sab kuch ( khail ke tor par nahi balkay ) ba maqsad hi banaya hai woh apni nshanyon ko khol khol kar paish kar raha hai unn logon ke liye jo ilm rakhtay hain
10,6,"yaqeenan raat aur din ke ulat phair mein aur har uss cheez mein jo Allah ne zameen aur asmano mein peda ki hai, nishanain hain unn logon ke liye jo ( ghalat beeni o ghalat rawi se ) bachna chahtay hain"
